Interface MavenActivationOSDescriptor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.buschmais.jqassistant.core.store.api.model.Descriptor, MavenDescriptor

    @Label(value="ActivationOS")
public interface MavenActivationOSDescriptor
extends MavenDescriptor
    Descriptor for an activator which will detect an operating system's attributes in order to activate its profile.

    ronald.kunzmann@buschmais.com
